    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你没在酒吧工作过？没事儿，Frank 就是干这活儿的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让他给那些口干舌燥的客人上几杯精酿啤酒，洗洗杯子，擦擦桌子，气氛搞起来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/edadba99cd5f4ea72f47aede3eb81600.poster.avif?t=1760114005\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/edadba99cd5f4ea72f47aede3eb81600.webm?t=1760114005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/edadba99cd5f4ea72f47aede3eb81600.mp4?t=1760114005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要记清楚客人是要新鲜的IPA，果味儿的菠萝奶昔酸，还是说一杯皮尔森就行？要注意是否有人因你上酒慢而开始抱怨了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搞些爆米花，让他们开心点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑动的时候千万别把杯子打碎了，不然你得花时间去收拾残局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级技能，解锁新的啤酒和吧台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another Bar Game 是3-4小时的酒吧疯狂体验！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/7015ff9ef8e3b7e2463da33f5188a5cc.poster.avif?t=1760114005\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/7015ff9ef8e3b7e2463da33f5188a5cc.webm?t=1760114005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/7015ff9ef8e3b7e2463da33f5188a5cc.mp4?t=1760114005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有人把包落在这里了？你要怎么处理呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/6af016bb0ad3ba348c2da7ff1952198d.poster.avif?t=1760114005\" width=350 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/6af016bb0ad3ba348c2da7ff1952198d.webm?t=1760114005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216060/extras/6af016bb0ad3ba348c2da7ff1952198d.mp4?t=1760114005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
